<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Raghav Code | Motivation, Discipline, Lifestyle</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<style>
    /* Base Styles */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
}

body {
    background-color: #0f0f0f;
    color: #f4f4f4;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Navigation */
nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 50px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
    position: fixed;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 1000;
}

.logo {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #e5ff00; /* Electric Yellow */
    letter-spacing: 2px;
}

.nav-links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
}

.nav-links a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.3s;
}

.nav-links a:hover {
    color: #e5ff00;
}

/* Hero Section */
#hero {
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517836357463-d25dfeac3438?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80') center/cover;
    padding: 0 20px;
}

.hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: #ccc;
}

.cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 15px 30px;
    background: #e5ff00;
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 5px;
    transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
}

.cta-btn:hover {
    background: #cce600;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
}

/* General Section Styling */
section {
    padding: 80px 50px;
    text-align: center;
}

h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    color: #e5ff00;
    text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* Cards (Tips & Tricks) */
.card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
}

.card {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border-top: 4px solid #e5ff00;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
}

.card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
}

.card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
}

/* Videos */
.video-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
}

.video-wrapper {
    background: #222;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 10px;
}

/* Transformation */
.subtitle {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #aaa;
}

.transform-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
}

.transform-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    max-width: 800px;
}

.image-placeholder {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    background: #333;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #777;
    font-weight: bold;
    border: 2px dashed #555;
    border-radius: 10px;
}

/* Footer */
footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #000;
    color: #555;
}

/* Mobile Responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 15px;
    }
    .nav-links {
        margin-top: 15px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
    }
    .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
}
</style>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">THE RAGHAV CODE</div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#tips">Discipline</a></li>
            <li><a href="#videos">Videos</a></li>
            <li><a href="#transformation">Transformation</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <header id="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>CRACK THE CODE TO A BETTER YOU</h1>
            <p>Motivation gets you started. Discipline keeps you going. Join the lifestyle.</p>
            <a href="#videos" class="cta-btn">Watch Latest Videos</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="tips">
        <h2>The Core Pillars of Discipline</h2>
        <div class="card-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>The 9-to-5 Fasting Window</h3>
                <p>Discipline starts on the plate. Confining your nutritional intake to a strict 9 AM to 5 PM window builds metabolic flexibility, mental clarity, and absolute control over your impulses.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Relentless Forward Progress</h3>
                <p>Whether it's pushing your distance on the track or logging daily miles, running is the ultimate metaphor for life. It's just you, the road, and the mental fortitude to keep moving forward.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Ultimate Sweat</h3>
                <p>Mastery requires repetition. Carving out time for dedicated, focused Hard Traning and Yoga makes your mind for long-term focus and consistency.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="videos">
        <h2>Latest from The Raghav Code</h2>
        <div class="video-grid">
            <div class="video-wrapper">
                <iframe width="100%" height="500" src="https://www.youtube.com/shorts/6BAbnFGO5TA" title="YouTube video" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="video-wrapper">
                <iframe width="100%" height="500" src="https://youtube.com/shorts/U9hfYEM0DPk?si=auKSjXq0OmAM9lZ6" title="YouTube video" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="video-wrapper">
                <iframe width="100%" height="500" src="https://youtube.com/shorts/6BAbnFGO5TA?si=RyQE4oiUGaahei-i" title="YouTube video" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="transformation">
        <h2>The Journey So Far</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">Proof that the code works.</p>
        <div class="transform-grid">
            <div class="transform-card">
                <div class="image-placeholder">Before Image Here</div>
                <div class="image-placeholder">After Image Here</div>
                <p>From day one to today. Consistency is the ultimate life hack.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 The Raghav Code. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
<script>
    // Add a dynamic background effect to the navbar on scroll
window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    const nav = document.querySelector('nav');
    if (window.scrollY > 50) {
        nav.style.boxShadow = '0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)';
    } else {
        nav.style.boxShadow = 'none';
    }
});
</script>
</html>
